WHAT
====
An X11 cursor theme loosely inspired on Windows 3.x cursors.


WHY
===
The lack of spinning hourglasses in today's design trends
for mouse cursors is absolutely revolting.


WHAT DO YOU NEED
================
ImageMagick and xcursorgen (part of the x11-apps package);
just cd to source and 'make'. If everything goes well, you
will be given a tar.bz2 file with the full theme, which will
also remain unpacked in a newly-created 'Hackneyed' folder.


